and customers would pour in like crazy!

00:24:15.240 --> 00:24:17.760
- No doubt we're gonna make insane sales!
- True.

00:24:25.640 --> 00:24:28.360
So many customers today!

00:24:28.720 --> 00:24:30.320
I'm almost shattered to pieces.

00:24:31.120 --> 00:24:33.640
You couldn't typically stand
my company, could you?

00:24:34.380 --> 00:24:36.320
Suddenly, you took on such a burden.

00:24:36.560 --> 00:24:38.600
You must have been very uncomfortable.

00:24:39.440 --> 00:24:41.160
Jeez, A-Mah!

00:24:41.480 --> 00:24:43.920
You're not a burden.

00:24:44.480 --> 00:24:47.440
It's you who couldn't
stand my company, isn't it?

00:24:48.880 --> 00:24:52.000
Do you not love me

00:24:52.440 --> 00:24:53.680
because I'm a granddaughter?

00:24:54.480 --> 00:24:56.680
I love my grandchildren equally.

00:24:58.480 --> 00:25:00.040
It's because you are a woman,

00:25:01.120 --> 00:25:02.880
like I am a woman.

00:25:03.800 --> 00:25:04.800
I know too well

00:25:04.840 --> 00:25:06.920
how much harder it is for us women

00:25:07.440 --> 00:25:09.320
to achieve anything at all.

00:25:09.560 --> 00:25:12.160
We have to fight
ten times harder than men.

00:25:13.200 --> 00:25:14.200
So how could I

00:25:14.360 --> 00:25:18.880
bring up a granddaughter
like I did a grandson?

00:25:22.860 --> 00:25:24.240
But do you know that

00:25:25.240 --> 00:25:30.000
it's much different now
compared to when you were young?

00:25:30.920 --> 00:25:33.880
We women can do everything

00:25:33.920 --> 00:25:35.200
just like men can.

00:25:47.600 --> 00:25:48.800
Look at me.

00:25:49.320 --> 00:25:52.000
I run this business all alone.

00:25:52.040 --> 00:25:53.960
You name it, I do everything.

00:25:54.760 --> 00:25:57.000
But I've got your help today.

00:25:58.800 --> 00:25:59.800
You're right about that.

00:26:04.920 --> 00:26:05.920
Hold on, A-Mah.

00:26:08.400 --> 00:26:09.600
Hello, Uncle?

00:26:11.040 --> 00:26:13.280
Jane, I'm here. Come out.

00:26:14.240 --> 00:26:15.160
Okay.

00:26:18.720 --> 00:26:19.560
Come on, A-Mah.

00:26:19.600 --> 00:26:20.600
Uncle is here to pick you up.

00:26:20.760 --> 00:26:22.080
Even when picking me up,

00:26:22.800 --> 00:26:24.120
he refuses to get out of the car.

00:26:24.560 --> 00:26:26.280
The door is just right there,

00:26:26.320 --> 00:26:27.320
so why not come?

00:26:29.240 --> 00:26:30.840
Come on, A-Mah. It's alright.

00:26:31.360 --> 00:26:33.200
When you get bored,

00:26:33.560 --> 00:26:36.040
you can stop by to help me sell shio pan.

00:26:36.960 --> 00:26:38.640
You won't get paid, though.

00:26:40.080 --> 00:26:42.040
It's alright. I have plenty

00:26:42.680 --> 00:26:43.610
thanks to these arms.

00:26:45.580 --> 00:26:46.360
Let's go, A-Mah.

00:26:46.400 --> 00:26:47.400
- Alright.
- Let's go.

00:26:47.960 --> 00:26:50.280
Come back whenever you have time.

00:26:50.520 --> 00:26:52.880
- Help me with the sales.
- Alright, alright.

00:27:15.240 --> 00:27:16.840
The sales aren't too shabby at all.

00:27:34.880 --> 00:27:38.080
Today, I won A-Mah's heart.

00:27:38.760 --> 00:27:39.600
How did I do?

00:27:40.220 --> 00:27:41.120
Good?

00:27:50.680 --> 00:27:51.600
Here.

00:27:52.000 --> 00:27:54.400
I made you a small one.

00:28:15.240 --> 00:28:16.320
There's a hair clip to go with it.

00:28:27.920 --> 00:28:29.080
That's adorable.

00:28:42.200 --> 00:28:44.000
I wish you were here with me...

00:29:07.040 --> 00:29:08.040
All done.

00:29:09.360 --> 00:29:13.040
Wow, you're all dolled up!

00:29:14.080 --> 00:29:15.520
May you make great sales today, dear.

00:29:15.840 --> 00:29:17.340
Sadhu!

00:29:17.520 --> 00:29:18.280
Abracadabra!

00:29:21.280 --> 00:29:23.200
I'll have to thank you

00:29:23.560 --> 00:29:26.280
for buying me three ovens.

00:29:26.320 --> 00:29:27.560
What a rich girl move.

00:29:32.880 --> 00:29:33.800
Thank you so much.

00:29:34.760 --> 00:29:36.240
Here you go.

00:29:37.560 --> 00:29:39.040
Let me go deliver the customer's orders.

00:29:39.320 --> 00:29:40.120
I'll be back.

00:29:41.880 --> 00:29:43.440
Please take care
of the shop and A-Mah while I'm gone.

00:29:43.480 --> 00:29:44.280
Sure thing.

00:29:44.880 --> 00:29:45.600
I'll be back.

00:29:46.240 --> 00:29:47.320
Be safe.

00:29:47.360 --> 00:29:48.560
I'll be right back.

00:29:51.640 --> 00:29:52.880
Here you go.

00:29:53.000 --> 00:29:54.200
Thank you so much.

00:29:54.240 --> 00:29:55.640
Enjoy your bread.

00:29:57.600 --> 00:29:59.880
Help me! Someone stole my purse!

00:29:59.920 --> 00:30:01.640
Give it back!

00:30:17.640 --> 00:30:18.440
Z!

00:30:32.800 --> 00:30:34.360
Excuse me, excuse me...

00:30:37.760 --> 00:30:38.960
Mission complete.

00:30:40.440 --> 00:30:41.360
Thank you.

00:30:42.240 --> 00:30:43.080
Thank you.

00:31:52.120 --> 00:31:54.320
[Song Wat]

00:32:08.400 --> 00:32:09.240
Z!

00:32:37.220 --> 00:32:38.500
Where have you been?

00:32:42.800 --> 00:32:44.120
I couldn't miss you more.

00:32:48.520 --> 00:32:49.680
Who are you, Miss?

00:32:51.000 --> 00:32:52.040
Do we know each other?

00:32:53.520 --> 00:32:54.400
What?!

00:32:54.680 --> 00:32:55.800
It's Jane!

00:32:56.600 --> 00:32:57.440
Jane!

00:33:00.200 --> 00:33:01.640
Are you messing with me?

00:33:01.680 --> 00:33:03.200
I noticed it from earlier, too.

00:33:03.600 --> 00:33:04.640
Don't play.

00:33:04.920 --> 00:33:05.920
I can see right through you.

00:33:06.840 --> 00:33:07.520
Huh?

00:33:10.360 --> 00:33:12.000
What?! You...

00:33:12.620 --> 00:33:14.400
You lived with me for a long time,

00:33:14.520 --> 00:33:16.200
we baked every day,

00:33:16.480 --> 00:33:18.640
and we even hung out at Song Wat!

00:33:23.240 --> 00:33:24.360
I'm sorry,

00:33:24.560 --> 00:33:25.800
but I think...

00:33:26.080 --> 00:33:27.680
you got the wrong person.

00:33:55.320 --> 00:33:56.840
She really doesn't remember me?

00:34:03.040 --> 00:34:06.320
Welcome, Jane,
to the Lucky Points system.

00:34:09.320 --> 00:34:12.600
I wish for Angel Z to come back to me.

00:34:12.639 --> 00:34:14.520
[A longing wish:
Please specify three wishes]

00:34:20.760 --> 00:34:21.840
- Ta-da!
- What?!

00:34:24.239 --> 00:34:25.239
Who are you?

00:34:26.600 --> 00:34:28.120
I'm a Z-ranked angel.

00:34:28.280 --> 00:34:29.880
You asked for me.

00:34:31.360 --> 00:34:32.360
This isn't right.

00:34:32.840 --> 00:34:34.000
I didn't ask for you!

00:34:34.360 --> 00:34:38.199
I meant Angel Z, who's a girl.

00:34:39.000 --> 00:34:40.120
And...

00:34:41.370 --> 00:34:44.409
she's blonde.

00:34:44.600 --> 00:34:47.080
Ugh, there are
so many angels in this rank.

00:34:47.639 --> 00:34:49.480
Just hurry up
and tell me what you need my help with.

00:34:57.440 --> 00:34:58.640
What? Uncle!

00:34:59.260 --> 00:35:00.560
My points are gone!

00:35:01.280 --> 00:35:03.280
Of course, you just made a wish.

00:35:04.400 --> 00:35:05.200
In that case,

00:35:06.600 --> 00:35:07.760
I'm sorry, Uncle.

00:35:08.360 --> 00:35:10.360
Jeez, Uncle this, Uncle that.

00:35:16.480 --> 00:35:17.360
Uncle!

00:35:18.200 --> 00:35:20.840
I wish to meet all the Z-ranked angels.

00:35:22.240 --> 00:35:23.680
Come on in!

00:35:42.200 --> 00:35:44.160
Is this everyone in the Z rank?

00:35:44.600 --> 00:35:45.920
Yes, we have everyone here.

00:35:46.120 --> 00:35:51.200
Well, what about
a girl with short blonde hair?

00:35:51.680 --> 00:35:53.760
The one who's a ball
of cuteness, you know?

00:35:54.000 --> 00:35:56.200
Oh, that kinda rings a bell.

00:35:56.240 --> 00:35:57.840
But it seems like she has moved,

00:35:57.880 --> 00:35:59.480
though I don't know if it's up or down.

00:36:02.280 --> 00:36:03.080
What?

00:36:05.320 --> 00:36:07.680
How can I ask for you back?

00:36:27.400 --> 00:36:29.240
I've tried all the wordings out there.

00:36:38.440 --> 00:36:42.400
I wish for the angel I love the most
to come spend forever with me.

00:36:42.440 --> 00:36:43.400
[Make a wish]

00:37:26.320 --> 00:37:27.240
Z?

00:37:53.920 --> 00:37:55.680
Ta-da!

00:37:56.520 --> 00:37:59.640
This is my very own shio pan shop!

00:38:02.600 --> 00:38:03.880
It's pretty nice.

00:38:07.240 --> 00:38:09.560
I told you

00:38:09.600 --> 00:38:11.720
that no matter what happened,
I'd open this shop.

00:38:14.200 --> 00:38:15.120
Remember?

00:38:27.640 --> 00:38:29.400
I took you here,

00:38:29.440 --> 00:38:30.760
and you still can't recall it?

00:38:36.580 --> 00:38:37.880
Not really.

00:38:45.080 --> 00:38:48.280
Did I say something wrong?

00:38:49.320 --> 00:38:50.320
Oh...

00:38:52.340 --> 00:38:53.340
You didn't.

00:38:54.320 --> 00:38:55.320
Uh...

00:38:55.820 --> 00:38:57.480
So, did you take me here

00:38:57.880 --> 00:38:59.160
because you need my help?

00:38:59.680 --> 00:39:00.600
You can tell me.

00:39:02.280 --> 00:39:03.200
Well,

00:39:04.080 --> 00:39:05.880
just having you with me is enough.

00:39:13.400 --> 00:39:14.400
I guess?

00:39:28.080 --> 00:39:29.400
Hi!

00:39:31.480 --> 00:39:32.480
Auntie Bew.

00:39:33.400 --> 00:39:35.320
I just happened
to be running errands nearby,

00:39:35.480 --> 00:39:37.720
so I'm stopping by
to buy some desserts for my mom.

00:39:38.040 --> 00:39:39.680
Oh...

00:40:20.320 --> 00:40:21.240
Bew?

00:40:25.240 --> 00:40:26.240
No...

00:40:28.960 --> 00:40:29.960
Mom?

00:40:41.640 --> 00:40:43.440
Beam is finally back with us.

00:41:16.940 --> 00:41:18.080
What is it?

00:41:20.200 --> 00:41:21.200
Nothing.

00:41:26.920 --> 00:41:28.280
How do you feel?

00:41:29.960 --> 00:41:30.600
Hm?

00:41:32.480 --> 00:41:33.480
Well,

00:41:34.840 --> 00:41:36.760
I'm talking about
when you met Auntie Bew earlier.

00:41:40.120 --> 00:41:41.440
It felt nice.

00:41:42.040 --> 00:41:43.280
I reunited with my mom after all.

00:41:46.800 --> 00:41:49.240
And since you remember her,

00:41:50.440 --> 00:41:51.360
what about me?

00:41:51.680 --> 00:41:52.680
Do you finally know who I am?

00:41:59.000 --> 00:42:00.440
It doesn't really ring a bell...

00:42:07.760 --> 00:42:10.440
Well, try thinking long and hard.

00:42:11.000 --> 00:42:13.240
We used to be so, so close.

00:42:13.400 --> 00:42:15.240
You lived in my house,

00:42:15.280 --> 00:42:16.800
we talked every day,

00:42:17.160 --> 00:42:18.920
and we baked every day!

00:42:19.080 --> 00:42:20.480
It was so much fun!

00:42:20.760 --> 00:42:21.920
And...

00:42:22.320 --> 00:42:24.720
you liked lying down
and looking at my face.

00:42:24.760 --> 00:42:27.120
I loved dragging you around,

00:42:27.640 --> 00:42:28.800
and we...

00:42:30.200 --> 00:42:31.840
kissed so many times.

00:42:32.360 --> 00:42:33.240
That's enough.

00:42:36.200 --> 00:42:38.320
I don't think I'll remember it,
no matter how many times you say it.

00:42:39.840 --> 00:42:40.920
So just stop.

00:42:42.440 --> 00:42:43.520
It's making me uncomfortable.

00:43:08.760 --> 00:43:10.360
Do you really want me to share the bed?

00:43:13.120 --> 00:43:13.800
Mm.

00:43:17.160 --> 00:43:17.960
I forgot...

00:43:18.720 --> 00:43:19.600
Then...

00:43:21.060 --> 00:43:22.060
Just pick wherever.

00:43:49.840 --> 00:43:50.720
Z!

00:43:53.600 --> 00:43:54.760
Did you remove the apron?

00:43:55.160 --> 00:43:55.840
Mm.

00:43:57.360 --> 00:43:58.440
Why?

00:43:59.640 --> 00:44:01.560
Well, it was weird to see,

00:44:01.880 --> 00:44:02.760
so I did.

00:44:18.800 --> 00:44:20.760
I'm gonna make you some breakfast.

00:44:22.800 --> 00:44:23.800
I'm not gonna stop.

00:44:30.760 --> 00:44:32.720
Yesterday, you told me to stop.

00:44:33.560 --> 00:44:34.560
I refused.

00:44:35.440 --> 00:44:36.200
Huh?

00:44:37.480 --> 00:44:39.400
I used a hundred thousand points
to redeem you back,

00:44:39.920 --> 00:44:41.040
so why should I stop?

00:44:41.080 --> 00:44:42.080
I'm not gonna stop!

00:44:44.080 --> 00:44:45.000
Listen.

00:44:45.820 --> 00:44:47.480
Whatever I tell you to do,

00:44:47.520 --> 00:44:48.640
you have to do it.

00:44:49.200 --> 00:44:51.320
If I tell you to remember me,

00:44:51.360 --> 00:44:52.720
you have to remember me!

00:45:16.520 --> 00:45:17.520
Hey!

00:45:17.800 --> 00:45:19.840
Every day, this was how
you kneaded the dough.

00:45:20.120 --> 00:45:20.960
Remember?

00:45:23.880 --> 00:45:24.640
Look,

00:45:25.160 --> 00:45:27.120
this is my special shio pan recipe.

00:45:29.800 --> 00:45:30.520
Here.

00:45:36.240 --> 00:45:37.000
What do you think?

00:45:37.680 --> 00:45:39.080
Does the taste ring a bell?

00:45:43.960 --> 00:45:44.760
No.

00:45:57.240 --> 00:45:58.360
Try listening to this.

00:46:01.800 --> 00:46:07.440
♫You secretly got my head in the clouds♫

00:46:07.880 --> 00:46:13.240
♫Your smile almost got me on the ground♫

00:46:13.280 --> 00:46:14.200
Come on.

00:46:15.760 --> 00:46:17.160
Sing it for me.

00:46:19.640 --> 00:46:20.880
It's the first time I've ever heard it.

00:46:21.440 --> 00:46:22.440
I don't think I can.

00:46:28.920 --> 00:46:29.600
Look,

00:46:30.540 --> 00:46:33.400
remember where we used to hang out?

00:46:45.160 --> 00:46:46.320
No...

00:46:53.280 --> 00:46:55.600
We used to lounge right here.

00:46:58.720 --> 00:46:59.720
And you...

00:47:01.400 --> 00:47:02.680
rested your head on my shoulder like so.

00:47:07.920 --> 00:47:09.200
And we...

00:47:10.280 --> 00:47:11.560
took photos like this.

00:47:14.080 --> 00:47:15.120
It's just like last year.

00:47:17.600 --> 00:47:18.400
Look.

00:47:22.060 --> 00:47:24.040
Can you remember it?

00:47:39.200 --> 00:47:40.000
Okay,

00:47:40.880 --> 00:47:41.680
it's fine.

00:47:45.920 --> 00:47:47.080
Let's hold hands like so.

00:47:47.840 --> 00:47:49.080
Jump in sync with me.

00:47:51.040 --> 00:47:51.680
Let's go.

00:47:53.280 --> 00:47:54.120
Okay!

00:47:56.960 --> 00:47:58.240
And...

00:48:12.280 --> 00:48:13.480
Come here.

00:48:30.560 --> 00:48:31.440
Z,

00:48:32.720 --> 00:48:33.720
do you remember it now?

00:48:42.880 --> 00:48:44.080
I'm sorry, Jane.

00:48:53.240 --> 00:48:54.000
Mm.

00:48:56.360 --> 00:48:57.360
It's fine.

00:48:59.560 --> 00:49:02.480
Just... take it slow.

00:49:03.040 --> 00:49:05.160
I'm sure it'll come back.

00:49:20.280 --> 00:49:22.040
Then, tomorrow,

00:49:22.340 --> 00:49:24.280
I'll take you
to more places we used to go

00:49:24.400 --> 00:49:25.560
in case you recall anything.

00:49:27.480 --> 00:49:28.200
Mm.

00:49:32.440 --> 00:49:33.520
[Music rehearsal room, third floor]

00:50:10.720 --> 00:50:12.320
There's no reason to try anymore.

00:50:21.440 --> 00:50:22.280
Come here!

00:50:31.960 --> 00:50:33.680
Whoa, Z!

00:50:38.360 --> 00:50:39.160
Z...

00:50:49.080 --> 00:50:50.080
Are you okay?

00:50:51.720 --> 00:50:52.720
Are you hurt?

00:50:54.000 --> 00:50:55.240
Does your head still hurt?

00:51:05.360 --> 00:51:06.280
Jane...

00:51:16.800 --> 00:51:17.800
Don't tell me...

00:51:20.000 --> 00:51:20.880
that you...

00:51:27.160 --> 00:51:28.240
I remember everything.

00:51:32.840 --> 00:51:34.720
I remember everything about us, Jane.

00:51:50.160 --> 00:51:51.280
I'm so happy...

00:52:34.800 --> 00:52:35.560
Right?

00:52:40.440 --> 00:52:41.880
Congrats!

00:52:42.000 --> 00:52:44.640
Finally, your memory came back.

00:52:45.120 --> 00:52:46.280
- Ate!
- Ate!

00:52:46.560 --> 00:52:47.560
Congrats!

00:52:47.920 --> 00:52:49.000
Look at her.

00:52:49.160 --> 00:52:50.830
I guess she's even happier than you,

00:52:50.920 --> 00:52:52.400
judging from that silly grin!

00:52:53.120 --> 00:52:54.060
- Auntie Itt!
- Ooh!

00:52:58.840 --> 00:52:59.760
Adorable couple, aren't they?

00:53:00.720 --> 00:53:01.120
Argh!!

00:53:01.160 --> 00:53:01.680
- Eek!
- Whoa!

00:53:01.720 --> 00:53:03.120
- Wait a minute...
- Ugh!

00:53:03.160 --> 00:53:04.240
- What?
- What was that?

00:53:04.480 --> 00:53:06.000
Since her memory is back,

00:53:06.040 --> 00:53:08.080
wouldn't this be another punishable violation?

00:53:08.600 --> 00:53:09.360
- You're right.
- You have a point.

00:53:09.400 --> 00:53:10.400
- I didn't think about that...
- Argh...

00:53:10.440 --> 00:53:11.640
No way!!

00:53:12.680 --> 00:53:13.840
He has a point...

00:53:29.400 --> 00:53:31.400
No worries!

00:53:33.360 --> 00:53:34.480
- Uncle Duang!
- Uncle Duang!

00:53:36.720 --> 00:53:38.280
How's it hanging, Uncle?!

00:53:39.560 --> 00:53:43.480
Your memory coming back
this time around isn't a violation

00:53:43.660 --> 00:53:45.600
since it was force majeure.

00:53:46.040 --> 00:53:50.000
Not a single soul has the right
to take you in for punishment!

00:53:53.360 --> 00:53:54.160
Is this true?

00:53:54.280 --> 00:53:55.280
Are you punking me?

00:53:55.640 --> 00:53:57.560
It's nothing but the truth!

00:53:57.600 --> 00:53:58.720
Plus,

00:53:59.760 --> 00:54:02.520
I'm not the same old Duang-Jai anymore.

00:54:04.460 --> 00:54:05.560
Why not?

00:54:13.840 --> 00:54:14.680
What's that?

00:54:16.180 --> 00:54:20.000
Right now, I have taken over
Miss Kaew-Ta's position!

00:54:20.160 --> 00:54:22.320
I guarantee that
I'm a hundred times more kind-hearted!

00:54:22.360 --> 00:54:24.560
Don't worry, be happy!

00:54:24.600 --> 00:54:26.880
- Yay!
- Yay!

00:54:29.880 --> 00:54:30.880
Don't worry.

00:54:33.080 --> 00:54:34.080
Uhh, who's that?

00:54:35.080 --> 00:54:36.080
Jane?

00:54:36.600 --> 00:54:37.600
Jane, sweetie?

00:54:38.280 --> 00:54:39.360
Who is he?

00:54:43.160 --> 00:54:45.680
I'm Duang-Jai,
the new leader of the angels.

00:54:45.880 --> 00:54:47.720
- Ooh!
- Right!

00:54:47.760 --> 00:54:51.040
I never knew that angels...

00:54:51.200 --> 00:54:52.800
- look like this.
- Right?

00:54:52.840 --> 00:54:54.120
He kinda looks like that one singer.

00:54:54.160 --> 00:54:55.320
He's totally your type, girl!

00:54:55.560 --> 00:54:57.080
Doesn't he look like Joke So Cool?

00:54:57.120 --> 00:54:58.720
He looks just like him!

00:54:58.960 --> 00:54:59.960
- Ooh!
- Isn't he?

00:55:03.600 --> 00:55:04.880
Here's your drink.

00:55:17.160 --> 00:55:21.280
[I want to die]

00:55:27.680 --> 00:55:28.920
I didn't order that.

00:55:29.560 --> 00:55:31.160
It's a special gift from us.

00:55:33.160 --> 00:55:34.720
Our shio pan

00:55:35.040 --> 00:55:37.640
can literally warm your entire heart.

00:55:37.960 --> 00:55:40.280
Anytime you don't feel your best,

00:55:41.280 --> 00:55:43.400
try filling your stomach
with something yummy

00:55:44.160 --> 00:55:45.800
and take a little nap.

00:55:46.680 --> 00:55:48.840
That might just make you feel that

00:55:49.240 --> 00:55:54.840
living in this world
is the most valuable gift out there.

00:56:01.560 --> 00:56:02.800
Enjoy your dessert.

00:56:09.800 --> 00:56:14.400
I introduce you to
'Six-Degrees Shio Pan Set'!

00:56:15.680 --> 00:56:17.520
This is the first degree,

00:56:17.840 --> 00:56:20.880
an avocado-filled shio pan.

00:56:20.920 --> 00:56:24.520
This was inspired by the moment
we filmed the MV with Miss Clare.

00:56:24.760 --> 00:56:27.960
- It tastes a little astringent, salty,
- You're gonna act funny to win her back!

00:56:28.000 --> 00:56:28.920
and tart...

00:56:29.360 --> 00:56:30.520
but all well-balanced.

00:56:32.200 --> 00:56:34.120
The second-degree shio pan

00:56:34.160 --> 00:56:35.560
is one with pineapple and kimchi filling.

00:56:35.860 --> 00:56:37.960
That sounds... odd.

00:56:38.280 --> 00:56:40.160
It was inspired by our meeting with Tom.

00:56:40.200 --> 00:56:42.560
Remember? Master Satanfah

00:56:42.760 --> 00:56:44.800
was both chaotic and messy,

00:56:45.120 --> 00:56:47.640
like these two ingredients
that don't supposedly seem to go well

00:56:48.160 --> 00:56:49.680
but surprisingly do.

00:56:50.200 --> 00:56:52.760
- When fate smiles on you, luck favors you!
- When fate smiles on you, luck favors you!

00:56:53.540 --> 00:56:55.760
Up next is the third degree.

00:56:55.920 --> 00:56:58.400
It's shio pan
with brownie and dark chocolate.

00:56:58.760 --> 00:57:01.200
This was when we spent the night
with the ghost for Pai!

00:57:03.080 --> 00:57:04.280
I was scared to death,

00:57:04.840 --> 00:57:07.720
but in the end, we curled up together,

00:57:09.880 --> 00:57:13.680
just like the bittersweet taste
this chocolate has to offer.

00:57:14.080 --> 00:57:15.400
What about the fourth degree?

00:57:15.860 --> 00:57:17.960
Shio pan with smoked salmon filling

00:57:18.000 --> 00:57:20.040
inspired by when we met Tony.

00:57:20.520 --> 00:57:24.480
I was really happy
that I got to sing on that stage,

00:57:24.720 --> 00:57:26.200
so I picked salmon

00:57:26.520 --> 00:57:30.160
because it's my favorite in the world!

00:57:31.480 --> 00:57:32.600
Totally biased!

00:57:34.520 --> 00:57:37.200
This is the fifth degree,

00:57:37.500 --> 00:57:39.640
coffee-almond-filled shio pan.

00:57:40.120 --> 00:57:42.240
Do you remember
when we met up with my mom?

00:57:42.680 --> 00:57:43.440
Mm-hm.

00:57:44.040 --> 00:57:46.600
That was such a bitter moment.

00:57:47.560 --> 00:57:48.800
I could only feel my tears.

00:57:49.400 --> 00:57:51.760
But I'm glad that I truly found her.

00:57:53.120 --> 00:57:55.040
Then what about the sixth degree?

00:57:55.240 --> 00:57:57.800
Shio pan with strawberry
and whipped cream filling.

00:57:58.120 --> 00:58:00.600
Sweet and heavenly,

00:58:01.440 --> 00:58:02.440
just like our relationship.

00:58:05.980 --> 00:58:07.960
My sixth degree

00:58:08.280 --> 00:58:09.400
is you.

00:58:10.900 --> 00:58:12.560
And your sixth degree

00:58:12.960 --> 00:58:13.960
is me.

00:58:18.280 --> 00:58:19.520
Therefore,

00:58:20.560 --> 00:58:22.440
this shio pan

00:58:23.240 --> 00:58:25.200
will embody our love.

00:58:30.400 --> 00:58:31.560
I love you, Z.

00:58:34.560 --> 00:58:35.880
I love you, too, Jane.

00:59:21.320 --> 00:59:23.040
Three, two, one!

00:59:31.640 --> 00:59:32.720
You're so cute.

00:59:36.600 --> 00:59:38.000
Love is reeking in the air!

00:59:47.480 --> 00:59:49.800
What are you looking at, singles?

00:59:50.400 --> 00:59:52.440
- Wow!
- Whoa!

00:59:52.920 --> 00:59:54.040
Alright!